QuestData.Title: Smuggled!
QuestData.Description: Please get me out of here!$b$bThe bars are brittle but I am so weak...$b$bThe others! There are so many others! Please help us!
QuestData.LogDescription: Release Maribeth and 5 captives in Felsoul Advance.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you. We had no hope of rescue before you came along.
